{"tid":2408882,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得自己係一個廢人","createTime":"2021-02-15T10:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T10:48:25.000Z","uid":381626,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7363d2461a07fb66755f2874782b877716c88e01","tid":2408882,"uid":381626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"覺得自己好無用 成個廢人咁<br />\n本人我無一個專長 讀書唔勁 可以話廢<br />\n簡單英文字眼 都未必識<br />\n中學嘅時候更發現自己有讀寫障礙 <br />\n集中唔到 聽嘢要比正常人聽多幾次先聽明<br />\n寫嘢都1999咁<br />\n<br />\n性格又唔好 只可以話自己對人開朗<br />\n除左成日係人面前笑之外 無咩優點<br />\n做事成日唔認真 唔識諗後果<br />\n<br />\n因為屋企得我一個<br />\n所以我係一個溫室長大嘅人<br />\n屋企人因為學業 一直唔比我返pt<br />\n直到我dse完<br />\n依家差唔多20歲先返得過一份pt<br />\n<br />\n我依嗰人無咩可用之處<br />\n見到同我同年紀都有D出色嘅時候<br />\n嗰種自我對比感覺 仲犀利<br />\n<br />\n我好想努力比其他人 比自己睇<br />\n我係有能力照顧自己<br />\n係成熟嘅<br />\n但喺最後結果都係 要人擔心 要人幫手<br />\n永遠都好似小朋友咁<br />\n<br />\n最近更發現自己有D抑鬱傾向<br />\n但喺唔想身邊愛我嘅人擔心<br />\n變得好少講出黎<br />\n唔想多交流<br />\n係人面前繼續滿帶笑容<br />\n<br />\n其實我係咪因為抑鬱症先變成咁 <br />\n諗嘢好負面 成日郁啲就喊<br />\n<br />\n唉 到底我可以點做"},{"pid":"baa4ca182ca37535a01595d77a8521f8c15ea3a6","tid":2408882,"uid":391931,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:25:08.000Z","msg":"防止自殺服務熱線<br />\n如你需要援助或協助有需要人士時，請致電以下求助熱線。同時，也請鼓勵你認為有需要協助的人士致電熱線取得協助。<br />\n香港<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4ecls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=47b93fa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sbhk.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbhk.org.hk&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4ecls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=3538e795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.sbhk.org.hk</a> <br />\n電話：2389 2222<br />\n<br />\n撒瑪利亞會 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.samaritans.org.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.samaritans.org.hk&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4ecls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=a737bb6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.samaritans.org.hk</a> <br />\n電話：2896 0000<br />\n<br />\n投注熱線<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkjc.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkjc.com&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4ecls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=5343bafd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkjc.com</a><br />\n電話：1881"},{"pid":"e2e7ddde82a05095afb0e62fb7a27934413d18d9","tid":2408882,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:25:08.000Z","msg":"咁。。。你想點？"},{"pid":"dd9d495667d648bf32117cb839150b47a89c531a","tid":2408882,"uid":328316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"點解樓主咁慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時D人開PO話自己抑鬱想死自殺<br />\n<br />\n就算係因為感情問題 或者自己衰on9 賭錢賭到冇錢還<br />\n<br />\n都會成班人衝入黎講好聽說話<br />\n<br />\n但係樓主一開PO即刻俾#2 串 \\<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/"},{"pid":"0fb8dd3a56c58ce41e83b554b927d1200b16659c","tid":2408882,"uid":328316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2e7ddde82a05095afb0e62fb7a27934413d18d9","tid":2408882,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:25:08.000Z","msg":"咁。。。你想點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:31:29.000Z","msg":"你收皮啦你你同我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd234ec0f500610c120cb2da799e4d115ea0611b","tid":2408882,"uid":328316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T10:32:45.000Z","msg":"你放心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到你屋企人發現你個人乜都做唔到, 自閉抑鬱 ETC 既時候<br />\n佢地就會調轉槍頭怪返你轉頭<br />\n老豆老母全部都係無恥"},{"pid":"7d37879969eda3524764f2d7ff6998defd2625d7","tid":2408882,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd9d495667d648bf32117cb839150b47a89c531a","tid":2408882,"uid